# Use Cases

- Use cases are are implemented in the application layers `src/Capability/<Name>/UseCases/<UseCaseName>.php`.

## Specification Block

Every use case class must document all of methods with a first line `Specification:`, followed by an empty line, then followed by a list of things the use case does, only behavior, business logic should be described here.

### Specification Block Example

```php
/**
 * Specification:
 *
 * - First line
 * - Second line
 *   - Sub-line
 */
class SomeUseCase
{
   //...
}
```
